36
00:03:10,550 --> 00:03:11,740
Aku hanya ingin, oke?

37
00:03:20,420 --> 00:03:21,580
Orang tuamu

38
00:03:22,790 --> 00:03:24,140
keduanya harus sangat lembut,

39
00:03:28,830 --> 00:03:29,740
