67
00:04:59,660 --> 00:05:00,500
Aku sudah lupa

68
00:05:00,500 --> 00:05:01,740
bahwa mereka telah pergi.

69
00:05:03,300 --> 00:05:04,150
Aku bahkan bisa

70
00:05:07,990 --> 00:05:08,940
